Google Colab, and then you can put it through the same pipeline. Now, in this case, there's no,

00:08:18.079 --> 00:08:22.079
by default, we do not re-execute the Jupyter notebook. This is one characteristic of Jupyter

00:08:22.079 --> 00:08:27.600
